# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
# Libraries should not include pubspec.lock, per https://dart.dev/guides/libraries/private-files#pubspeclock.
/pubspec.lock
**/doc/api/
.dart_tool/
build/

# rust/ is the vendored copy of crates/whitenoise-frb/ used by cargokit when
# the package is consumed standalone (orphan branch). On master we keep the
# canonical source under crates/whitenoise-frb/. Developers who need a local
# Flutter build can symlink with: `just frb-vendor-link`.
/rust/
